\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-linkedin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z\"></path><rect width=\"4\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"9\"></rect><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>LinkedIn</a></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#0F1A14]/80\"><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Christopher is a global fixture in the philanthropic space with extensive experience in leading sustainable community empowerment initiatives and managing large-scale internatinoal projects from inception to completion. </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">He has successfully guided cross-functional, multicultural teams, drawing on over 30 years of hands-on experience in Latin America, Africa, and Southeast Asia. </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Throughout his career, he has worked closely with local facilitators to implement anti-poverty strategies rooted in core values, leadership development, community ownership, and self-determination. </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">One of Christopher&#x27;s key passions is combining mission and purpose with the discipline and efficiency of business to create impactful tools that address unmet needs in financially sustainable and scalable ways.</p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Outside of his professional life, Christopher is an avid mountain biker, cyclist, hiker, runner, and adventurer. Whether he’s exploring new places, diving into innovative technologies, or learning from the wisdom and insights of his three incredible children, </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Christopher finds fulfillment in the experience of learning and connecting with others.</p></div></div></div></div><!--$--